Oslo, August 31st;;2011;;Not Rated;;Drama;;7.6;;Joachim Trier;;Anders Danielsen Lie,Hans Olav Brenner,Ingrid Olava,Malin Crépin,Aksel Thanke,Øystein Røger,Tone Beate Mostraum,Kjærsti Odden Skjeldal,Petter Width Kristiansen,Emil Lund,Johanne Kjellevik Ledang,Renate Reinsve,Andreas Braaten,Anders Borchgrevink,Lennart Anker,Anna Liljeroth,Line Eikenes,Arne Rasmussen;;Anders is a recovering drug addict in an Oslo rehab clinic. On 30 August, he is given a day's leave to attend a job interview in the city center. After visiting his friend Thomas, he proceeds to his appointment. In the interview, he admits to being a drug addict and storms out. He then wanders the streets of Oslo for the rest of the day and night, meeting, and sometimes confronting, people from his past. The film ends the next day, 31 August. Focusing on the decisions Anders has made with his time off.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1736633/